HEADWORD: Telodynamic
<hw>Tel`o*dy*nam"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ far +
E. <ets>dynamic</ets>.]</ety> <def>Relating to a system for transmitting
power to a distance by means of swiftly moving ropes or cables driving
grooved pulleys of large diameter.</def>⟦br⟧
